title: Episode #44 - Women's Suffrage in New Zealand/Countess Markievicz/Switzerland
itunes:author: History Is Sexy
itunes:summary:
It's a three-in-one this time as Emma and Janina tackle three questions, all on the theme of Women's suffrage!

Why did New Zealand grant universal suffrage so early?
Who was the *real* first woman MP?
Why is Switzerland so weird?

Sources: https://historyissexy.com/show-notes/episode-44-womens-suffrage
